UPGRADE

Upgrading from versions 1.x, 2.0.x, 2.1.x, 2.2.x and 2.3.x is not
supported anymore. You will have to upgrade first to Campsite 2.6
or 2.7 and then follow the regular procedure.

Upgrading from Campsite 2.4.x and newer versions:
Repeat the following steps for each instance:

1. Backup the instance using campsite-backup-instance
2. Perform a new Campsite 3.0 install
3. Run the restore backup script from the admin interface


Read INSTALL file and follow the steps; read on Compatibility issues.


Compatibility issues

In version 3.0 the template language as modified extensively. The
backup restore script will provide an automated conversion of the old
template files to the new format. For more details on language changes
please read the manual.
